Go to Terminal
crontab -e
will open crontab editable file (select your editor to open the file)
add the following line to the end of file.

*/5 * * * * bash <path to Task2.sh>/Task2.sh 



Notes:
* means every
First * is for Mins (*/5 means every 5 mins) (0-59)
Second * is for Hours (1-24)
Third * is for days in a month (1-30)
Fourth * is for month (1-12)
Fifth * is for days in a week (1-7)


